Hey! It’s me, Tommy, and the best ceo in town, Puffles! 👋🏼 It’s been awhile since I’ve introduced myself on here, so I thought today would be a fun day to do just that! 
.
Here are a few fun facts about me: 
 .
🧶I’ve been crocheting since 2017. (Crazy, right?!) What started out as a hobby has transformed into a business and I’m very fortunate that I can do what I love on a daily basis. 
📺 In my personal opinion, Golden Girls is the best television show ever created. No matter how many times I rewatch it, I’ll never tire of Rose, Dorthy, Sophia, and Blanche’s adventures. 
🪷 I’m a big nature lover! Learning about different plant and animal species is one of my favorite hobbies. 
🎨 Speaking of learning, recently I’ve been reading about color theory. As a big fan of color, this has been a very interesting thing to read about! 
.
As for Puffles, I’m pretty sure she’s got treats on her mind. After every photo shoot she knows there’s a reward awaiting her. 🐱 
.
.
.
.
